snippet.title: Amberlynn Reid's ICONIC 2021 MOLMENTS
snippet.description:
It's been ONE YEAR since I uploaded my first video to this channel! I started this channel in a pandemic to deliver all the edits, compilations, commentary and comedy that I myself wanted to see in Haydur Nation! Now one year and 36 THOUSAND subscribers later we are going strong (despite *someone* trying to take us down)! Thank you to all woop woopers who are here watching every day, commenting your video wants/needs...I am *honored* to be the one to fulfill your haydur dreams 🤟🥺🙌


This video was made compiling many different videos and moments therefore changing the story line completely.
